<p>Go high this winter. These ski resorts have altitude as well as attitude.</p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55}" title="Insider's Guide: Best High Altitude Ski Resorts">Read more&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g3">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Most Family Friendly Resorts</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13070740/families-placeholder.jpg" alt="FAB 5 best ski resorts for families" data-udi="umb://media/f859561f78034d21908929e195b188f5" /></p>
